column5: Yesterday took my maiden voyage out on Lake O. for some Salmon.  Thanks JSW if you are on this board.  Thanks for everones help and advice.  Here is my personal best and first lake O Salmon.
AWESOME!!!     First of many I'm sure...and a beauty at that
nice shooting ...welcome to the BIG GAME ....
Man what a beauty beast Congratulations on your PB Leechman
Nice fish and photo, you must have given the reel a bit of a workout with that one..
